name: Mysnb
body:
### Overview
This is a collection of spark notebooks for my own use. You may find it useful as well, but I give no warranty whatsoever. I have used these notebooks on MacOS with the new Mac Docker engine (still beta). Highly experimental.

### Authors and Contributors
Tobias Abarbanell (@abarbanell) 

### Support or Contact
I have tried to add explanations in the notebooks and the readme of the master branch. Beyond that - may the source be with you.
